      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>Hello, adventurer!<BR>It's been awhile since I brought you news about <FONT color=#086171>new events</FONT>.<BR>
I am happy to tell you about a new event called <FONT color=#a82424>Best Hero Tournament</FONT>!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-a" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, I heard about it. </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-b" mid="30" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>No, I haven't….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>Have you heard about <FONT color=#a82424>Best Hero Tournament</FONT> already?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-c" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>That's great!<BR>The Royal Palace hasn't been holding any events for some time so everyone must be excited about it.<BR>But you would still want to hear the details from me, wouldn't you?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-c" mid="32" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>I see. It's been awhile since the Royal Palace held its last event so I thought they were actively promoting it….<BR>I guess I need to step it up. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-d" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>As you can guess from the name, Best Hero Tournament is for finding the best hero in Saint Haven…<BR>No, I should say the best hero in Lagendia continent. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-e" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>What you have to do is to battle against powerful creatures handpicked by the high-ranking court officials.<BR><FONT color=#086171>General Douglas</FONT>, <FONT color=#086171>Court Sorceress Kayleen</FONT>, and <FONT color=#086171>Duke Stuart</FONT> will be the judge. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-f" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>I heard Kayleen has a terrible monster up her sleeve.<BR>If you manage to defeat all the enemies… <BR>You are entitled to battle against a <FONT color=#a82424>hidden opponent</FONT> and stand a chance to get <FONT color=#a82424>special rewards</FONT>! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-g" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>If you're worried whether your opponents will be too strong, fret not!<BR>The judges will keep their eyes on the tournament and make the  battle more interesting in <FONT color=#086171>various ways</FONT>. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-h" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Wouldn't that be against the purpose of holding the tournament?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>Maybe King Cassius himself will be there to support you.<BR>Wouldn't it be amazing if he bestows his royal blessings on you? </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-i" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What is it?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>Haha, don't worry.<BR>Although the Royal Palace is holding this event to pick skilled heroes…<BR>The tournament has a hidden purpose.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-j" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>As you might know, there have been many incidents and accidents so far.<BR>
That has made the atmosphere of Saint Haven gloomier than ever.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-k" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>So the real purpose of this event is to revitalize the city and provide the citizens with something to enjoy while identifying the finest heroes at the same time.<BR><FONT color=#2b2723>Entertainment</FONT> for the residents of Saint Haven, <BR><FONT color=#a82424>honour</FONT> and <FONT color=#a82424>rewards</FONT> for adventurers! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-l" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>So please feel free to come and enjoy yourself.<BR>The people of Royal Castle are all waiting for you, <FONT color=#387206>{user_class}</FONT> <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-m" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>You can enter <FONT color=#086171>Best Hero Tournament</FONT> from <FONT color=#2b2723>Saint Haven's East, West, and South Gate's</FONT><FONT color=#a82424> <BR></FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Best Hero Tournament Lobby</FONT><FONT color=#2b2723></FONT>.<BR>
Participating in a party would be the best so remember to bring like-minded companions along!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
